1. Clone into ~/Dropbox/Apps/ or edit DROPBOXFOLDER
2. Place your /Packages/ and /Installed Packages/ in the same folder.
3. ./init.sh

This script will
- Create symlinks in ~/Library/Application Support/Sublime Text 3/ for Packages and Installed Packages from your Dropbox folder, allowing you to sync your settings and packages across devices.
- Create a symlink for the Sublime Text binary in /usr/local/bin
